This Holocron seems to continiously play the image of a young human girl  who looks to be in her twenties, short cropped hair dyed purple decorates her head in a ponytail, a tattoo on her neck symbolizing she is a Sith yet her demeanor seems different, almost serene.

As if sensing your presence she looks to you, smiling.



[ Lyrael teaches that hatred is not the only emotion that may drive a Sith and asks for you to rephrase the Sith Code.]

    "Peace is a lie, there is only passion.
    Through passion, I gain Love.
    Through Love, I gain Companionship.
    Through Companionship, I gain Bliss.
    Through Bliss, my chains are broken.
    The Force shall free me." 
    --The Code of the Darth Ranimus

[ Passion is the first stepping stone cast into the pond of the Sith, it is the guiding force that leads to greater benefactors, but so many forget the original emotions that have driven them to their pure hatred.]

[Rather than letting Hatred consume you and to drive you to your own doom, embrace the Passion to your Freedom, may it be Love, which was mine, or any other that is your driving force.]

[For the Force shall free you, as it did I.]
